about-ironfox-title = The Book of Iron - 1:2
about-ironfox-from = Lähde: <strong>The Book of Iron,</strong> 1:2
about-ironfox-quote =
    And so, the <em>Mole</em> had fallen. As the <em>Beast</em> had already lost its way, the believers
    began to lose faith, and the world was left in <em class="f">darkness</em>. As hope was almost lost, a
    <em>Fox</em> created a<em class="f">spark</em>. Drawn to its<em class="f">light</em>, a<em>Phoenix</em> bonded
    with the <em>Fox</em> to form a special coat of<em>Iron</em>. With its newfound <em class="f">strength</em>, the
    creature rose to <em class="f">avenge</em> the<em>Mole</em> and the<em>Beast</em> that fell before it.
